_sText: ***** Old Version - New version can be found here. ***** I have recently found out that a map called gg_beachhouse already exists by someone else on FPSBanana. I am sorry for this, and have there renamed my map to gg_beach_house in respect of this. I apologise for not checking the name in advance properly. ***** ===== gg_beach_house_v01 by 'corruptSteel. ===== Concept Design by 'cS.*CitizeN^ErazeD** Map Creation by 'cS.Metz ===== Visit us at http://csclan.inx-gaming.co.uk ===== Update Log: v01 - Release version ===== This is the first map I have created for Counter-Strike: Source and is still a work-in-progress. Please download and enjoy this first version and let me know what you think of it, and if you have any ideas for improvements, please give feedback. Thanks, 'cS.Metz =====
